    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Simpro Overdue Quotes Workflow\n\n### Setup Instructions:\n\n1. **Configure OAuth2 Credentials:**\n   - Go to Credentials > Add Credential > OAuth2 API\n   - Set up your Simpro OAuth2 credentials\n   - Replace `YOUR_OAUTH2_CREDENTIAL_ID` with your credential ID\n\n2. **Update Company Information:**\n   - Replace `YOUR-COMPANY` with your Simpro subdomain\n   - Replace `YOUR_COMPANY_ID` with your actual Company ID\n\n3. **Configure Email Settings:**\n   - Set up SMTP credentials for sending emails\n   - Update the sender email address\n   - Customize the email template as needed\n\n4. **Adjust Overdue Threshold:**\n   - Default is 7 days\n   - Modify the `daysThreshold` variable in the filter node\n\n5. **Schedule:**\n   - Currently set to run daily at 9:00 AM\n   - Modify the cron expression in the Schedule Trigger node\n\n### Workflow Logic:\n\n1. Triggers daily at 9 AM\n2. Fetches all quotes from Simpro API\n3. Filters quotes overdue by 7+ days\n4. Attempts to get contact email (with customer fallback)\n5. Verifies email exists and is valid\n6. Sends formatted reminder email to each overdue quote\n\n### Notes:\n- The workflow handles both contact and customer email lookups\n- Includes error handling for missing emails\n- HTML email template is fully customizable\n- Supports pagination (default 250 quotes per request)",
        "height": 464.79532952920877,
        "width": 389.2722647050889,
        "color": 4
      },
      "name": "Sticky Note - Instructions",
